 the two plasma jets are utilized on\ncholangiocarcinoma xenograft tumor model developed in immunodeficient mice. The\ntwo devices are safe and a significant therapeutic efficiency is demonstrated\nwith the plasma Tesla. In conclusion, we have developed a safe cold atmospheric\nplasma device with antitumoral properties in preclinical model of\ncholangiocarcinoma, opening the path for new anticancer treatment\nopportunities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Nov 2019 16:32:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-26"}
