sional periodic\nFermi-Hubbard chain. These results promote the future use of q-UCC methods for\nthe solution of challenging electronic structure problems in quantum chemistry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Nov 2019 12:28:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2020 18:11:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-07"}
